{"title":"走过丰产路","authors":["张继楼"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":8,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过丰产路\t张继楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过丰产路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪个不停步："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向左看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“党委指挥田”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一眼望去数十亩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水满肥又足；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶儿宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秆儿粗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秧苗绿得发了乌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向右看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“三八高产坡”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包谷如林已成熟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"株株背包三、四个。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包谷正收割，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苕藤封了坡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一队妇女下坡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑语声声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗筐装满丰收乐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道两旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见一寸荒废土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瓜藤绊住脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豇豆爬上行道树；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个南瓜露大肚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吊吊豇豆像流苏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芝麻、绿豆、向日葵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄黄绿绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高矮矮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像开的百货铺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正惊叹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一溜牛车伊呀过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车车满载珍珠颗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞭梢响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起山歌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一条丰产路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个百宝窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社无限好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍珠宝贝用车拖。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}